channel.title: Lulz, NPC's disappeared
channel.description:
[s]All my NPC's are gone on my server, even though they're still in the autospawn.cfg and my height level is 0. I've restarted the client and server to no avail.
I'm also not getting any errors, such as a failure to load the autospawn or something along that line. I'm confused.[/s]
My client was making me think my height level was 0, but when I logged out it reset to -37. I went up 37 times and found them again.
